<br>
Lots of organizations are capable of that type of response, the KKK, the Hells Angels, The Bloods, The Crips, West Side Wilmas, do you expect those organizations to be loved, or even accepted by the communities they're in simply because their membership likes each other and supports one another?<br>
<br>
AS may have been a great close group of people who had a great time together, but so are the aforementioned groups.<br>
